{
  "stem": "20848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my mother said, what happened to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She said, I was so frantic, I was asking everybody where you were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they kept saying, oh, you're going to come, you're going to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But they knew that I was going-- I was put to gas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So this man that I have never ever seen before or after, he saved me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Out for years and years, I was thinking how come he came to me when there were so many people there, you know, children and women.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And a few years ago, I found out, it occurred to me that I must have drawn his attention to me by just constant going to the German guards and saying [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And those people-- he was a Jewish man, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They were working there, he must have noticed that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So when there was smoking a cigarette, he smuggled me out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I was three months in Majdanek with my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And there were selections all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a barrack, on a-- on a-- they were not [INAUDIBLE], they were bunk-- bunks, different to-- to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- there was a terrible lot of lice there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day, they were snatching people to go and work in a place called [GERMAN], which was a garden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very lucky, you know, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was a child, people took pity on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the camp was run by Polish women, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Polish women were very cruel to the Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But somehow, they were nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know why, they kept saying, how old are you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept saying, I'm 16.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they used to say, you're 16 like we are 80.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how it was, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
